'''B''' iga askkil wiss [[sin]] g u[[Agmmay alatin n tmaziɣt|gmmay n iskkiln imaziɣn]], askkil ad iga askkil alatin, acku ikkad tutlayt nɣ agmmay alatin. Mac urd [[Tutlayt Talatint|tutlayt talatint]] ka g illa, illa g tugt n tutlayyin g umaḍal, zund ukan tutlayyin n [[Urupa|Uruppa]], [[Marikan]] [[amnẓaw]], [[tafriqt]], [[asya]] ... Askkil ad illa ula g ugmmay agrik aqqbur.
Askkil '''B''' ur igi win igrikn nɣ win ilatinn, askkil ad iga yan uskkil ittyawssan dar kullu [[Aɣrf|iɣrfan]] iqqbuṛn zund [[ifrɛunen]], iṛumin ...

